{
  "stem": "26609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so he used to go very early in the morning, about, say, 5 o'clock in the morning or even earlier, through that [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Skotnik, ?] through there was a-- a way right to the station, but quite a long way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he had to pass-- there was a river and a bridge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember that, too, that bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On that bridge, he had to pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He went through that bridge, through this, and on this bridge to the station, about, I would say, 100 times.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was his-- not a profession, but that's what he did for living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "One morning, that Ukrainians, these boys and their father, they spied on him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They knew what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They didn't know exactly, but they knew that he's carrying a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He goes by train to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They caught him on the bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were two big, tall men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was-- that uncle was, he's about, say, 60-- between 50 and 60, older than my mother then, though not very strong.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They grabbed his bag with the money and threw him into the river.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He drowned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So they killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES] As he didn't come home-- back home, my auntie alarmed the police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He didn't come home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He told-- she told them that he carried money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He had money with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The police-- you see, also no one likes the Jews there, but not so far.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "If it's a crime, the police had to find out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The police with dogs [PAUSES] went around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They knew that no Jew would do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Opposite was that [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Skotnik. ?] They were Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But the dogs carried them to the house, right to that house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
